[Lowland and mountain-slope rainforests to scrub-steppe at elevations of 
<quantity id="036C9B1BFF4D6AF2F5DC914C1815BC6D" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.4" metricValueMax="2.6" metricValueMin="0.2" pageId="182" pageNumber="944" unit="m" value="1400.0" valueMax="2600.0" valueMin="200.0">200- 2600 m</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
